name: BabyManyu
description: BabyManyu ($BABYMANYU) is the playful successor to the viral $MANYU on Ethereum, carrying forward the legend of Manyu the Mame Shibe. Just as Doge inspired BabyDoge, BabyManyu emerges as the “baby version” of $MANYU—backed by a passionate community, fresh believers, and meme culture at its core. With an ambitious roadmap featuring BabyManyu Swap, Launchpad, NFTs, and even bridge integrations, the project blends fun with forward-looking utility. Whether you’re here for memes, community, or opportunity, BabyManyu is more than a token—it’s the next chapter in Ethereum’s dog-coin legacy.
